     (New usage is discouraged.) $)
  merlem4 $p |- ( ta -> ( ( ta -> ph ) -> ( th -> ph ) ) ) $=
    ( wi wn ax-meredith merlem3 ax-mp ) AADBEZIDDBDZCDCADBADDZDCKDAABBCFKJCGH
    $.

  $( Step 11 of Meredith's proof of Lukasiewicz axioms from his sole axiom.
