       [Lopez-Astorga] p. 12 , rule 4 on [Sanford] p. 39 and rule A4 in
       [Hitchcock] p. 5 .  (Contributed by David A. Wheeler, 3-Jul-2016.)
       (Proof shortened by Wolf Lammen, 12-Nov-2017.) $)
    mpto2 $p |- -. ps $=
