       (Proof modification is discouraged.) $)
    mtp-xorOLD $p |- ps $=
      ( wn wb wxo df-xor mpbi bicom mtbi xor3 mpbir ) BAEZCBAFZEBNFABFZOABGPEDA
      BHIABJKBALIM $.
  $}

