    19.9v $p |- ( E. x ph <-> ph ) $=
      ( wex ax17e ax-17 19.8w impbii ) ABCAABDABABEFG $.

    $( Special case of Theorem 19.3 of [Margaris] p. 89.  (Contributed by NM,
