       by Wolf Lammen, 7-Aug-2017.) $)
    spimw $p |- ( A. x ph -> ps ) $=
      ( weq wn wal wi ax9v spimfw ax-mp ) CDGHCIHACIBJCDKABCDEFLM $.
  $}

  ${
