       definitions, see ~ dffun2 , ~ dffun3 , ~ dffun4 , ~ dffun5 , ~ dffun6 ,
       ~ dffun7 , ~ dffun8 , and ~ dffun9 .  (Contributed by SF,
       5-Jan-2015.) (Revised by Scott Fenton, 14-Apr-2021.) $)
