        20-Apr-2021.) $)
     dmsnfn $p |- dom ( x e. A |-> { x } ) = A $=
       ( cv csn cvv wcel crab wa cab cmpt df-rab eqid dmmpt snex biantru abbi2i
       cdm 3eqtr4i ) ACZDZEFZABGSBFZUAHZAIABTJZQBUAABKABTUDUDLMUCABUAUBSNOPR $.
  $}

